{"tid":2487982,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國民兵「小藍人」扮漁民闖南海 CNN：規模之大讓人擔憂","createTime":"2021-04-14T02:32:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T05:25:36.000Z","uid":39464,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"12cd749d5498d1124d22a43893cb072c4cad2a90","tid":2487982,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T02:32:45.000Z","msg":"有主權爭議的南海繼續受國際關注，220艘中國漁船早前在菲律賓以東的牛軛礁（Whitsun Reef），不僅引起菲律賓當局抗議，更讓當區局勢持續緊張。美國有線新聞網絡（CNN）報道，中國有一支政府始終不承認的海上民兵「小藍人」（Little Blue Men）部隊，這些民兵的船隻堅固、裝載自動化的武器，還比世界上90%的漁船都還要快，這個中國不願承認的部隊正日益擴張，規模已經達到令人憂心的程度。<br />\n<br />\n根據《CNN》報導 ，中國220艘重型漁船日前大舉入侵南海牛軛礁，引來菲律賓嚴厲抗議，並指稱船上人員為中國海上民兵。對此，中國外交部發言人華春瑩表示當時僅為一些漁船躲在牛軛礁附近避風，是正常的行為；中國駐菲律賓大使館更直接否認，聲稱「中國根本沒有海上民兵組織」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210414/7YPDK2E5WFEQJL3QO5CYYALCNI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210414%2F7YPDK2E5WFEQJL3QO5CYYALCNI%2F&d=anIIoOx73pQIzJB4hJH11AwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=3825ac3a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210414%2F7YPDK2E5WFEQJL3QO5CYYALCNI%2F&h=2e916d25\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210414/7YPDK2E5WFEQJL3QO5CYYALCNI/</a>"},{"pid":"f895b877e4d53fe6c2f8f83edf9cfff492fc5439","tid":2487982,"uid":357030,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T02:40:35.000Z","msg":"小藍人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79283f9acbe978e62a1261c8bb590ef33bd164b4","tid":2487982,"uid":54125,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T02:41:34.000Z","msg":"已經島都起緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d4a683f3a2ed2135264e5aa792417e77d5d414e","tid":2487982,"uid":282637,"